---
// Hero section with animated badge and CTA buttons
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid z-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[400px] bg-white/[0.03] blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 w-full">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-xs font-medium text-neutral-300 mb-8 animate-fade-in opacity-0">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500"></span>
        </span>
        Disponible para proyectos freelance
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-medium text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-8 animate-fade-in delay-100 opacity-0">
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-200 to-neutral-600">Fullstack developer</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-400 max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 animate-fade-in delay-200 opacity-0">
        Desarrollo con Laravel, React y Node.js, y también diseño interfaces limpias, modernas y usables. Código sólido con estética profesional.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 animate-fade-in delay-300 opacity-0">
        <a href="#work" class="group relative px-6 py-3 bg-white text-black text-sm font-medium rounded-full overflow-hidden transition-all hover:pr-9">
          <span class="relative z-10">Ver Proyectos</span>
          <span class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 transform group-hover:translate-x-0 -translate-x-2">
            <span class="iconify text-black" data-icon="lucide:arrow-right" data-width="16"></span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/ivanmercedes" target="_blank" class="px-6 py-3 border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 text-neutral-300 hover:text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="iconify" data-icon="lucide:github" data-width="16"></span>
          GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce opacity-50">
    <span class="iconify text-white" data-icon="lucide:arrow-down" data-width="20"></span>
  </div>
</section>
